ings made from this\npaper provide insight into how MICP processes vary across a range of\ntemperatures and could be valuable for optimising the MICP process for\ndifferent applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Feb 2022 13:41:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-22"}
